Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.76,0:00:32.78,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你能想象身处难以置信的环境中的自己吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.76,0:00:32.78,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Have you ever found yourself in such as a real situation that you can hardly believe it's real?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.44,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我现在就和两位朋友坐在上百吨爆炸物上，准备前往太空
Dialogue: 2,0:00:33.30,0:00:39.44,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm currently sitting on top of tons of explosives with two great friends ready to be shot into space
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.44,0:00:43.78,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,即人类最大的火箭之一——阿丽亚娜五号
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.44,0:00:43.78,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,by one of humankind's biggest rockets: the mighty Ariane 5.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:45.66,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,真是不错的一天呀
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.86,0:00:45.66,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Perfectly normal day, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.90,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我是Bepi，上面一起的是Mio
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.90,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm Bepi and together with Mio up there
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.90,0:00:55.28,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们将在内太阳系进行一次伟大的旅程，最终前往水星
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.90,0:00:55.28,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We're going on a great adventure through the inner solar system to planet Mercury
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.90,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,当然，也不能忘了我们的朋友MTM
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.90,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,But let's not forget about our robot friend MTM
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.90,0:01:02.74,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,他将负责在星箭分离后带我们一路前往水星
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.90,0:01:02.74,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,who after this ride on the rocket is going to carry us all the way there.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.74,0:01:06.80,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这次旅程将花费七年，一路飞跃其他行星数次
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.74,0:01:06.80,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,A journey that will take seven years flying past other planets along the way
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.32,0:01:11.80,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们选水星的目的不是因为那是什么旅游胜地
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.32,0:01:11.80,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We certainly didn't pick Mercury because it's the most hospitable destination out there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.72,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而是因为那里有很多未解之谜等着我们去解决
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.72,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,but because there are still so many unsolved questions about this mysterious world.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.34,0:01:21.14,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们一生都在为此次旅行做准备
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.34,0:01:21.14,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Our whole lives have been spent getting ready for this great adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.76,0:01:55.96,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,在学校里，老师们因材施教，让我们扬长避短
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.76,0:01:55.96,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We worked very hard in school each bringing our own contribution to the mission
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.40,0:02:00.38,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,虽然只有我和Mio要去探索水星的未解之谜
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.40,0:02:00.38,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Even though it will just be me and Mio investigating Mercury's mysteries.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.58,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,但我们要靠MTM才能去水星
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.58,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It will be up to MTM to get us there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.22,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,没有他可靠的发动机我们根本飞不了那么远
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.22,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We would not get far without our trusty engine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.86,0:02:11.10,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,同样，我们的老师在让我们准备发射前往水星的路途上也功不可没
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.86,0:02:11.10,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,The same is true for all of our teachers getting us ready for launch and our journey towards the Sun
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.72,0:02:15.10,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,水星那会很热，就像披萨烤箱一样
Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.72,0:02:15.10,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It's going to be very hot at times, like working in a pizza oven
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.76,0:02:19.66,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,MTM和我要穿上特别的衣服来防止晒伤
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.76,0:02:19.66,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,MTM and I needed to get special jackets fitted to protect us.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.94,0:02:23.82,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而Mio则有更新奇的方法防止在水星过热
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.94,0:02:23.82,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Well, Mio invented a novel way to keep cool once at Mercury
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.06,0:02:27.86,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,她会不停自转来均匀接受来自太阳的热
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.06,0:02:27.86,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,She's going to spin around to evenly distribute the sun's heat,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.02,0:02:31.88,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,但在路上，她会一直呆在一个太阳罩内
Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.02,0:02:31.88,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,but on the way, she will have to sit still inside a Sun shield
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.56,0:02:38.10,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,除了数学、物理和各种工程知识
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.56,0:02:38.10,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,As well as math, physics and engineering
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.16,0:02:40.64,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们还要学习各自的语言
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.16,0:02:40.64,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We also started to learn each other's languages
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.72,0:02:45.88,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Mio来自日本，对欧洲的各个国家和语言充满好奇
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.72,0:02:45.88,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Mio is from Japan and is very curious about all the different countries and languages in Europe
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.12,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而我也在学习日语
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.12,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,while I try to learn some Japanese
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.44,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们慢慢开始了解彼此文化的差异
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.44,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We began to understand some of the differences between our cultures
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.44,0:02:56.74,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这对我们未来几年的共同旅行、工作非常重要
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.44,0:02:56.74,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,which is important because we will spend many years traveling and working together
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.90,0:03:06.04,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,整个旅途中我们还要进行很多轨道机动，这是要练习很多次的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.90,0:03:06.04,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Throughout the journey we will need to make a lot of manoeuvres and these had to be practiced over and over
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.02,0:03:13.46,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们将飞跃地球一次、金星两次、水星六次，最终环绕水星
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.02,0:03:13.46,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We will fly by Earth once, Venus twice and even Mercury six times before orbiting around it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.34,0:03:24.78,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,想象一下，我们将是人类第一个同时探索水星的两个探测器
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.34,0:03:24.78,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Just imagine, we will be the first mission to study planet Mercury with two spacecraft at the same time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.98,0:03:28.66,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,两个好朋友将一起进行很多伟大的实验
Dialogue: 2,0:03:24.98,0:03:28.66,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Two friends planning to do some great experiments together.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.98,0:03:36.76,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我曾对我未来的旅程满怀憧憬，但我也承认我还是有点害怕的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.98,0:03:36.76,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I was always fascinated by our destination, but I confess I used to be a bit afraid of it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.12,0:03:42.76,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,如此刁钻的轨道与离太阳的咫尺之遥让此次旅程犹如刀山火海
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.12,0:03:42.76,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Such an odd orbit and being so close to the Sun made it really difficult to get to
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.92,0:03:46.14,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,水星是内太阳系探索得最少的行星
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.92,0:03:46.14,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It was the least explored planet in the inner solar system
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.38,0:03:49.50,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,但那一晚，一切都变了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.38,0:03:49.50,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,But one night changed everything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.50,0:03:55.16,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我突然克服了我的恐惧，甚至深深着迷于此
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.50,0:03:55.16,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I quickly overcame my fears and became completely captivated
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.16,0:04:00.38,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,着迷于我将来的旅程——那将是几乎不曾有探测器涉足过的地方
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.16,0:04:00.38,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,by the thought of travelling to this strange world that so few spacecraft had braved before
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.64,0:04:05.62,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我等不及要亲眼看看那个世界，想了解那里为什么和地球与众不同
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.64,0:04:05.62,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wait to see it with my own eyes and to understand why it was so different to Earth
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.90,0:04:13.44,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,在我们渐渐长大的时候，表亲信使号传回了水星很多有趣的发现
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.90,0:04:13.44,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,As we were growing up our cousin Messenger sent back news of many interesting discoveries on Mercury
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.32,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,反而让我们更加好奇！
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.32,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Which left us quite curious!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.40,0:04:22.06,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我对撞击坑的火山喷发与构造活动等地质过程很感兴趣
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.40,0:04:22.06,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm really interested in geological processes like Impact cratering Volcanic eruptions and tectonic activity
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.06,0:04:27.54,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,以及其如何在数十亿年来改变了行星表面的化学组成和地貌
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.06,0:04:27.54,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and how that changes the chemistry and appearance of a planet's surface over billions of years
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.86,0:04:31.90,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Mio最喜欢研究磁场和宇宙射线
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.86,0:04:31.90,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Mio's favorite subjects are magnetic fields and space plasmas
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.72,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,以及太阳如何影响行星所处的环境
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.72,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and studying how the Sun influences the planet's environment.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.20,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这实际上算是我们的共同目标
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.20,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That's actually something we're both going to do.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.28,0:04:44.62,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,——从不同角度去探索太阳风如何与行星磁场相互作用
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.28,0:04:44.62,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Investigate how the solar wind interacts with a planet's magnetic field from our two different viewpoints.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.80,0:04:50.94,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,水星是如此赤裸裸的星球，我们将研究太阳和小型陨石
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.80,0:04:50.94,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Mercury is a rather exposed planet and we would be able to see how the Sun and small meteorites
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.04,0:04:55.76,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,如何改变水星表面和我们轨道周围环境的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.04,0:04:55.76,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,change the conditions both down there and in the environment along our orbits.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.86,0:05:01.70,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我相信我们将看到很多改变，我们也很兴奋能同心协力
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.86,0:05:01.70,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It certainly sounded like we would see lots of changes and we were excited to bring our skills together
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.94,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,以一个完整的系统来让我们更好地了解水星
Dialogue: 2,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.94,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,to better understand the planet as a complete system.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.62,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,有无数未解之谜在等待着我们
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.62,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,There are certainly still plenty of mysteries to solve
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.06,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,是时候出发啦
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.06,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It's almost time to go
